#:''I will open the shop an hour early tomorrow.''
# {{transitive}} To [[start]] (a campaign).
# {{intransitive}} To become [[open#Adjective|open]].
#:''The door opened.'' 
# {{intransitive}}  To begin conducting business.
#:''The shop opens at 9:00.''
